= Taur Matan Ruak( 路路 ) = Mntucing hngkawas 1956 idas 10 jiyax 10 ka Taur Matan Ruak ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bukung klwaan Timor-leste ta sayang o kiya ka Taur Matan Ruak, pnaah hngkawas 2012 idas 5 jiyax 19 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
